!!!
%html{:lang => "en"}
  %head
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}/
    %meta{:content => "IE=edge", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}/
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}/
    %meta{:content => "", :name => "description"}/
    %meta{:content => "", :name => "author"}/
    %title Mellow Miles
    / Fonts
    %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}/
    %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Josefin+Slab:100,300,400,600,700,100italic,300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}/
    / HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries
    / WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file://
    /[if lt IE 9]
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
  %body
    .brand Mellow Miles
    .address-bar Mellow Miles Cycles, 67 Victoria Road, Horley, Surrey, RH6 7QH
    / Navigation
    %nav.navbar.navbar-default{:role => "navigation"}
      .container
        / Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display
        .navbar-header
          %button.navbar-toggle{"data-target" => "#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :type => "button"}
            %span.sr-only Toggle navigation
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
          / navbar-brand is hidden on larger screens, but visible when the menu is collapsed
          %a.navbar-brand{:href => "/"} Mellow Miles
        / Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling
        #bs-example-navbar-collapse-1.collapse.navbar-collapse
          %ul.nav.navbar-nav
            %li
              %a{:href => "index.html"} Home
            %li.dropdown
              %a.dropdown-toggle{"aria-expanded" => "false", "data-toggle" => "dropdown", :href => "#", :role => "button"}
                Bikes
                %span.caret
              %ul.dropdown-menu{:role => "menu"}
                %li
                  %a{:href => "about.html"} Racing bikes
                %li
                  %a{:href => "about.html"} Mountain bikes
                %li
                  %a{:href => "about.html"} Children's bikes
                %li
                  %a{:href => "about.html"} Folding Bikes
                %li
                  %a{:href => "about.html"} Town bikes
            %li
              %a{:href => "about.html"} Accessories
            %li
              %a{:href => "about.html"} Servicing
            %li
              %a{:href => "about.html"} Contact Us
        / /.navbar-collapse
      / /.container
    .container
      .row
        .box
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            #carousel-example-generic.carousel.slide
              / Indicators
              %ol.carousel-indicators.hidden-xs
                %li.active{"data-slide-to" => "0", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                %li{"data-slide-to" => "1", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                %li{"data-slide-to" => "2", "data-target" => "#carousel-example-generic"}
              / Wrapper for slides
              .carousel-inner
                .item.active
                  %img.img-responsive.img-full{:alt => "", :src => "../images/slide-1.jpg"}/
                .item
                  %img.img-responsive.img-full{:alt => "", :src => "../images/slide-2.jpg"}/
                .item
                  %img.img-responsive.img-full{:alt => "", :src => "../images/slide-3.jpg"}/
              / Controls
              %a.left.carousel-control{"data-slide" => "prev", :href => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                %span.icon-prev
              %a.right.carousel-control{"data-slide" => "next", :href => "#carousel-example-generic"}
                %span.icon-next
            %h2.brand-before
              %small Welcome to
            %h1.brand-name Mellow Miles
            %hr.tagline-divider
            %h2
              %small
                The Cycle website.
      .row
        .box
          .col-lg-12
            %hr/
            %h2.intro-text.text-center
              A Cycle Shop
              %strong worth visiting
            %hr.tagline-divider
            %hr/
            %img.img-responsive.img-border.img-left{:alt => "", :src => "../images/rbp.jpg"}/
            %hr.visible-xs/
            %p For most people, riding a bicycle is introduced to us at a very young age and for many people it is their earliest memory of experiencing success and achievement – do you remember the first time you rode your bike without assistance? The thrill as a child of riding your bike with friends and the freedom it offered you?
            %p
              Well, at Mellow Miles Cycles we firmly believe that cycling should be enjoyed by everyone, regardless of age, physical fitness or working commitments...
              %a{:href => "http://join.deathtothestockphoto.com/", :target => "_blank"} Read more -->

      .row
        .box
          .col-lg-12
            %hr/
            %h2.intro-text.text-center
              %strong What We Offer
            %hr.tagline-divider
            %img.img-responsive.img-border.img-left{:alt => "", :src => "../images/mb.jpg"}/
            %hr.visible-xs/
            %p As an independent cycle shop, Mellow Miles are not restricted or incentivised to sell you a specific make of bike or accessory, unlike many larger shops and chains. Our guidance and advice is entirely impartial and we guarantee that your best interests are our number 1 concern.
            %a{:href => "http://join.deathtothestockphoto.com/", :target => "_blank"} Read more -->

      .row
        .box
          .col-lg-12
            %hr/
            %h2.intro-text.text-center
              %strong Who We Are
            %hr.tagline-divider
            %img.img-responsive.img-border.img-left{:alt => "", :src => "../images/np.jpg"}/
            %hr.visible-xs/
            %p Mellow Miles Cycles is owned and run by Nigel Brown, a former British Cycling champion and a man who has spent his entire adult life working in the cycle industry. Whilst we stock and sell many leisure bikes at extremely competitive prices, we are specialist retailers of some of the best cycle brands in the World including Basso, Moda, Ridgeback and Forme.
            %a{:href => "http://join.deathtothestockphoto.com/", :target => "_blank"} Read more -->

            
    / /.container
    %footer
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            %p Copyright © Jack Sharville
    :javascript
      $('.carousel').carousel({
          interval: 5000 //changes the speed
      })